an to obtain more quasars from\nfuture observations and establish a complete faint quasar sample with more than\n1000 objects over 10 deg^2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Feb 2006 23:28:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
